statements: SELECT * FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data;
SELECT timestamp, sensor_reading FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data;
SELECT sensor_id, arm_position_x, arm_position_y FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data ORDER BY sensor_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data WHERE sensor_reading > 50;
SELECT sensor_id, timestamp, arm_position_z FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT sensor_id, arm_position_x, arm_position_y FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data WHERE sensor_reading > 0.5 ORDER BY timestamp ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT AVG(sensor_reading) AS avg_reading, MAX(sensor_reading) AS max_reading FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data GROUP BY sensor_id HAVING COUNT(sensor_id) > 10
SELECT sensor_id, timestamp, arm_position_z FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data WHERE arm_position_x < 0 AND arm_position_y < 0
SELECT * FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31' ORDER BY sensor_reading DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data;
SELECT sensor_id, timestamp FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT position_x, position_y, position_z FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data WHERE sensor_id = 3;
SELECT sensor_id, MAX(timestamp) AS latest_timestamp FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data;
SELECT analysis_id, analysis_result FROM robotic_arm_analysis WHERE analysis_result LIKE '%fault%';
SELECT sensor_id, timestamp, position_x, position_y, position_z FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data WHERE sensor_id = 1
SELECT analysis_id, sensor_id, analysis_result FROM robotic_arm_analysis ORDER BY analysis_id DESC
SELECT * FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data WHERE position_x < 0 AND position_y > 0 ORDER BY timestamp ASC
SELECT analysis_id, sensor_id, analysis_result FROM robotic_arm_analysis WHERE analysis_result LIKE '%error%'
SELECT sensor_id, position_x, position_y FROM robotic_arm_sensor_data WHERE position_z BETWEEN -1.0 AND 1.0
SELECT * FROM sensor_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT sensor_id, temperature FROM sensor_data WHERE arm_position='up';
SELECT MAX(temperature) AS max_temperature FROM sensor_data;
SELECT * FROM arm_calibration WHERE angle > 90 AND torque < 20;
SELECT DISTINCT calibration_id, efficiency FROM optimization_results WHERE cost < 1000 ORDER BY efficiency DESC;
SELECT * FROM sensor_data WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND temperature > 25 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT sensor_id, arm_position, temperature FROM sensor_data WHERE arm_position IN ('up', 'down') AND temperature BETWEEN 20 AND 30 ORDER BY temperature ASC;

SELECT s.sensor_id, a.calibration_id, a.angle, o.efficiency FROM sensor_data s INNER JOIN arm_calibration a ON s.sensor_id = a.sensor_id INNER JOIN optimization_results o ON a.calibration_id = o.calibration_id WHERE o.efficiency > 0.8 ORDER BY o.efficiency DESC, a.angle ASC;
SELECT * FROM arm_calibration WHERE angle = 90 OR angle = 180 AND torque > 50;
SELECT * FROM sensor_data WHERE arm_position = 'up' AND TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, timestamp, NOW()) > 3600;
SELECT movement_id, timestamp, arm_id, movement_type, movement_value FROM robotic_arm_movements;
SELECT arm_id, movement_type, movement_value, timestamp, movement_id FROM robotic_arm_movements;
SELECT movement_type, movement_value, timestamp, movement_id, arm_id FROM robotic_arm_movements;
SELECT * FROM robotic_arm_movements WHERE arm_id = 1;
SELECT movement_type, movement_value FROM robotic_arm_movements WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM robotic_arm_movements ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT movement_type, movement_value FROM robotic_arm_movements WHERE arm_id = 1;
SELECT movement_id, timestamp, movement_type, movement_value FROM robotic_arm_movements WHERE movement_value > 100 ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT movement_type, COUNT(*) AS movement_count FROM robotic_arm_movements GROUP BY movement_type HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT timestamp, SUM(movement_value) AS total_value FROM robotic_arm_movements WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM robotic_arm_movements ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM arm_positions WHERE position_z > 0 ORDER BY position_x ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT id, movement_type, movement_intensity FROM robotic_arm_movements WHERE arm_id = 'arm001' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM sensor_readings WHERE sensor_id = 'sensor002' AND sensor_value > 10 ORDER BY timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM movement_history ORDER BY duration DESC, timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM robotic_arm_movements ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT movement_type, movement_intensity FROM robotic_arm_movements WHERE arm_id = 'A1' AND movement_intensity > 50;
SELECT * FROM arm_positions WHERE position_x < 0 AND position_y > 0 AND position_z = 0;
SELECT sensor_id, sensor_value FROM sensor_readings ORDER BY sensor_value DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM movement_history WHERE duration BETWEEN 1000 AND 2000;
